Halflings are a race of short people (hence the name) much given to 
the simpler pleasures in life, including good food, a warm bed, a 
window overlooking a pleasant little garden, a shady tree to lie 
under in the afternoon, and a full pipe after dinner.  They do not 
often become adventurers, but those that do are quite good at it.  
They are not too strong, because of their small size, and their 
homebody nature means they tend to be not as wary.  But halflings 
have truly incredible reflexes and are remarkably nimble and quick 
with their hands.  Halflings are most interested in having fun in life, 
and they take this attitude with them wherever they go.
 
Halflings are able to drink and eat more than the other races.

Halflings cannot join the following guilds:  Druid, Fighter.
